OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPartly
OL,6,Fcloudy and dry through the evening
OL,7,Fwith some thicker cloud moving
OL,8,Fsouthwards for eastern areas that
OL,9,Fcould give some localised light rain
OL,10,For drizzle over the Moors. A cooler
OL,11,Fnight inland with light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FA cloudy and dry day, perhaps
OL,14,Fwith the odd light shower over the
OL,15,Fhills. Mainly light winds, sunny
OL,16,Fspells developing through the
OL,17,Fafternoon. Temperatures around average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
