OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FPredominantly dry and partly cloudy
OL,7,Fthrough the period, with isolated
OL,8,Flight showers mainly over the hills
OL,9,Fand coast. Mainly light winds.
OL,10,FTemperatures around average to
OL,11,Fslightly above.
